---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import SecureFieldsCrumbs from '../../components/SecureFieldsCrumbs.astro';

const title = 'Support | Secure Fields';
const description = 'How to reach support for Secure Fields, including security vulnerability reports.';
---

<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <SecureFieldsCrumbs current="support" />

  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <p class="mb-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-signal">Support</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl tracking-wide text-bone md:text-5xl">Support</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">Secure Fields is built and supported by a small, hands-on team &mdash; reach out directly.</p>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-10 leading-relaxed text-muted">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide text-bone">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          <a href="mailto:jack@inorganicgames.com" class="text-signal underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-signal-dim">jack@inorganicgames.com</a>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          When you write in, it helps to include your Jira site URL, the name of the affected field, and a
          description of what you're seeing.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide text-bone">What we can help with</h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
          <li>
            Setup and configuration questions &mdash; see the
            <a href="/secure-fields/docs" class="text-signal underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-signal-dim">Setup &amp; Usage Guide</a>
            first for the most common ones.
          </li>
          <li>Bugs or unexpected behavior.</li>
          <li>
            Security vulnerability reports &mdash; please report these privately to the address above
            rather than filing a public issue. We commit to acknowledging reports promptly and to not
            taking action against good-faith security research.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide text-bone">Response time</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">We respond to all support requests as quickly as we can.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide text-bone">Looking for something else?</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          For questions about Inorganic Games LLC's other products (our TikTok Mini Games), contact
          <a href="mailto:inorganicgames@gmail.com" class="text-signal underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-signal-dim">inorganicgames@gmail.com</a>
          instead &mdash; the address above is dedicated to Secure Fields.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
